      "text": "Thunder Truck Rally (released as Monster Trucks in Europe) is a 1997 racing video game developed by Reflections and published by Psygnosis for the PlayStation and Microsoft Windows. Players select a monster truck or otherwise 4X4 vehicle equipped with monster truck tires and have the option of either racing or crushing cars in an arena.",
